title: Spittin' Chiclets Episode 182: Featuring Matt Duchene
description:
On Friday's episode of Spittin' Chiclets the guys are joined by Matt Duchene. Matt joins to talk about his upcoming free agency, the playoffs, the time he wouldn't take a shot with Whit and a bunch more. The guys also give a full recap of Game 5 and the Blues giant win and preview Game 6 in what could be the last game of the season.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/schiclets
